听了吴刚的台词，我都想再去做几份模拟卷了。
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200925/5dc04f7a1a1f43909f27131d68d93941.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
